<TEXT>
   Here are the top 50 entries in Fortune
magazine's fourth annual list of the world's billionaires with
name, home, source of wealth and estimated fortune in billions:
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
   1. Sultan of Brunei; oil and gas, real estate, foreign
investments; $25.
   2. King Fahd and family; Saudia Arabia; oil and gas; $18.
