   7. Yoshiaki Tsutsumi; Japan; railroads; $7.3.
   8. Sam M. Walton; Arkansas; Wal-Mart Stores; $7.3.
   9. John Werner Kluge; Virginia; Metromedia Inc., real estate,
investments; $7.0.
   10. Tsai Wan-Lin, Tsai Wan-tsai, and family; Taiwan: insurance
and construction; $6.5.
   11. Kenneth Roy Thomson and family; Canada; newspapers and real
